== 停飛 ==
2018年7月，母公司对国会表示，由于中共禁止大陸游客前往帕劳旅行，旅客数目减少，帕勞太平洋航空以商業理由停飛香港航線<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.businessinsider.com/palau-airline-closes-over-anger-from-china-about-taiwan-ties-2018-7|title=Palau airline closes over anger from China about Taiwan ties - Business Insider|work=[[Business_Insider|Business Insider]]|accessdate=19 July 2018|archive-date=2021-11-21|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20211121223827/https://www.businessinsider.com/palau-airline-closes-over-anger-from-china-about-taiwan-ties-2018-7|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=http://islandtimes.us/another-airline-out/|title=Another airline out?|date=13 July 2018|accessdate=19 July 2018|archive-date=2020-02-17|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200217205753/http://islandtimes.us/another-airline-out/|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

